{"type": "article", "id": 9044, "title": "智能脚踏板", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-30T07:16:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235049kMTC3f9jKc1hEsox.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t法国公司 Connected Cycle 推出了一款智能脚踏板。脚踏板内部装有GPS，安装在自行车上之后，可以自动追踪自行车的轨迹，进行行车记录，同时，脚踏板搭载防盗系统，可以向用户发送警告，并追踪自行车位置。脚踏板内置数据套餐，不需要通过蓝牙和手机连接，并且使用内置的机械装置自行发电。目前这款产品正在 Indiegogo 上众筹，感兴趣的大家可以<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/connected-cycle-pedals\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235046bRpEhrY2kXIutD5K.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.57962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235047QfNtWDqIcBSV5Xxs.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235047CP1bjnMQ8IWea24D.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235047QrgsHFe2q4PajvLd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.59351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}